[
  {
    "text": "♪ Mellow instrumental hip-hop ♪ ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=0"
  },
  {
    "text": "♪ ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=4"
  },
  {
    "text": "Justin Etzine: Welcome to \"Add SharePlay to your app.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=10"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm Justin Etzine from the SharePlay team. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=12"
  },
  {
    "text": "When people think of SharePlay, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=15"
  },
  {
    "text": "they often think about being on a FaceTime call ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=16"
  },
  {
    "text": "with their friends, watching a show, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=18"
  },
  {
    "text": "or listening to music together. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=20"
  },
  {
    "text": "In fact, these are the most popular types ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=23"
  },
  {
    "text": "of SharePlay experiences today. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=25"
  },
  {
    "text": "Many video streaming and music listening apps ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=28"
  },
  {
    "text": "support SharePlay, including Apple's own. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=30"
  },
  {
    "text": "Just press play, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=33"
  },
  {
    "text": "and you're in the activity together. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=34"
  },
  {
    "text": "But really, it's much more than that. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=36"
  },
  {
    "text": "SharePlay is all about any activity with any group. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=39"
  },
  {
    "text": "It can help bring groups to activities in apps ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=43"
  },
  {
    "text": "without needing to worry about accounts or servers. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=47"
  },
  {
    "text": "SharePlay can also be added to enhance shared experiences ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=50"
  },
  {
    "text": "already offered by your apps today. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=53"
  },
  {
    "text": "With a small amount of work to adopt, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=56"
  },
  {
    "text": "you can bring an instant start ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=58"
  },
  {
    "text": "with the group that's already there. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=59"
  },
  {
    "text": "And we believe privacy to be a fundamental human right. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=62"
  },
  {
    "text": "The powerful data channel ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=66"
  },
  {
    "text": "optimized and secured for FaceTime powers SharePlay too. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=67"
  },
  {
    "text": "This means GroupActivities provides ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=72"
  },
  {
    "text": "a fully end-to-end encrypted channel ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=74"
  },
  {
    "text": "for your app's data to pass through, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=76"
  },
  {
    "text": "and Apple cannot see any app data sent over SharePlay. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=78"
  },
  {
    "text": "Virtually every app offers opportunities for SharePlay. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=82"
  },
  {
    "text": "Any activity is better when you can share it with friends, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=86"
  },
  {
    "text": "and there, SharePlay can help. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=89"
  },
  {
    "text": "And with GroupActivities, the framework to adopt ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=92"
  },
  {
    "text": "for SharePlay, app teams small and large ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=94"
  },
  {
    "text": "can leverage everything they need ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=97"
  },
  {
    "text": "to get the group together to the activity ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=99"
  },
  {
    "text": "and to facilitate fast data transfer ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=101"
  },
  {
    "text": "between participants once in the activity. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=104"
  },
  {
    "text": "At its core, you bring the activity, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=108"
  },
  {
    "text": "and we'll bring the group. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=110"
  },
  {
    "text": "In this session, we'll cover some of the new products, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=113"
  },
  {
    "text": "technologies, and features coming to SharePlay. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=115"
  },
  {
    "text": "We'll tell you a bit about how they unlock new use cases, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=118"
  },
  {
    "text": "walk you through the benefits ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=122"
  },
  {
    "text": "of adopting SharePlay for your app, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=123"
  },
  {
    "text": "and offer advice on best practices ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=125"
  },
  {
    "text": "to get the most from SharePlay. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=127"
  },
  {
    "text": "Groups are often already together ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=130"
  },
  {
    "text": "when they use SharePlay. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=132"
  },
  {
    "text": "And the activity started may not be the experience ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=134"
  },
  {
    "text": "they stick with throughout their time together. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=137"
  },
  {
    "text": "One of the beauties of SharePlay is that it enables your apps ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=140"
  },
  {
    "text": "to take advantage of the group that's already present. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=143"
  },
  {
    "text": "SharePlay has been especially impactful for me with my family ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=147"
  },
  {
    "text": "living on the east coast of the United States. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=150"
  },
  {
    "text": "SharePlay helps me maintain a close connection ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=152"
  },
  {
    "text": "to my brother and parents. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=154"
  },
  {
    "text": "At first, we looked to connect those far away ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=156"
  },
  {
    "text": "through meaningful and fun experiences in your apps. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=160"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is why, when we first created SharePlay, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=163"
  },
  {
    "text": "we focused the experience of SharePlay in FaceTime calls. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=165"
  },
  {
    "text": "From there, we expanded SharePlay ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=170"
  },
  {
    "text": "so that it could be used with or without a call ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=172"
  },
  {
    "text": "with SharePlay via Messages. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=174"
  },
  {
    "text": "But beyond far away, often the group is right there ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=176"
  },
  {
    "text": "next to you, in the same room. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=179"
  },
  {
    "text": "We're thrilled to bring SharePlay over AirDrop ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=182"
  },
  {
    "text": "in iOS 17, where bringing your devices together ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=185"
  },
  {
    "text": "starts a SharePlay, just like that. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=188"
  },
  {
    "text": "One of my favorite parts of AirDrop is how easy it is ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=191"
  },
  {
    "text": "to find who you're trying to share with, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=194"
  },
  {
    "text": "since they're in the same room. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=196"
  },
  {
    "text": "Imagine even when you're next to somebody, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=198"
  },
  {
    "text": "jamming out on the subway with your friends, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=201"
  },
  {
    "text": "laughing at the funniest new memes, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=203"
  },
  {
    "text": "or finding your dream home with your partner ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=205"
  },
  {
    "text": "without having to look over one person's shoulder. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=207"
  },
  {
    "text": "No need to ask for their username or email to share. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=209"
  },
  {
    "text": "Just AirDrop and you're there, together. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=212"
  },
  {
    "text": "AirDrop joins FaceTime and Messages ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=216"
  },
  {
    "text": "as existing group contexts you can bring to SharePlay. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=218"
  },
  {
    "text": "And as the group moves, so does the SharePlay. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=221"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you start it nearby and move apart, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=224"
  },
  {
    "text": "you can keep the chat going in Messages. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=226"
  },
  {
    "text": "And hopping into a FaceTime call is just a tap away. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=229"
  },
  {
    "text": "And in tvOS 17, you can start your FaceTime call ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=233"
  },
  {
    "text": "on the big screen. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=236"
  },
  {
    "text": "From there, getting the SharePlay going ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=237"
  },
  {
    "text": "is just an app away. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=239"
  },
  {
    "text": "As you'll hear a bit later in the talk, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=241"
  },
  {
    "text": "this is a great example of why we encourage you ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=243"
  },
  {
    "text": "to bring SharePlay to your apps across the ecosystem, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=245"
  },
  {
    "text": "so that when the group moves ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=249"
  },
  {
    "text": "the experience can keep going without a hitch. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=250"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, when defining your GroupActivity type, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=254"
  },
  {
    "text": "you provide metadata to inform the system ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=256"
  },
  {
    "text": "on how to best represent your activity. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=259"
  },
  {
    "text": "For this order together here, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=262"
  },
  {
    "text": "we specify an activity type of generic. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=264"
  },
  {
    "text": "This type, among other things, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=267"
  },
  {
    "text": "tells the system HUD which icon to use: ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=269"
  },
  {
    "text": "Watching together, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=273"
  },
  {
    "text": "listening together, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=275"
  },
  {
    "text": "playing together through Game Center, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=276"
  },
  {
    "text": "or generic to indicate any other form ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=279"
  },
  {
    "text": "of SharePlay experience you can imagine. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=282"
  },
  {
    "text": "In iOS 17, iPadOS 17, macOS Sonoma, and tvOS 17, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=285"
  },
  {
    "text": "we're adding some additional types ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=290"
  },
  {
    "text": "to help best classify activities: ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=292"
  },
  {
    "text": "Workout, Shop, Read, Learn, and Create Together. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=295"
  },
  {
    "text": "We're excited to see how this helps illustrate ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=300"
  },
  {
    "text": "your exciting types of experiences, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=302"
  },
  {
    "text": "both now and to come. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=304"
  },
  {
    "text": "WWDC23 has some fantastic content ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=307"
  },
  {
    "text": "about how to use SharePlay in new ways. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=310"
  },
  {
    "text": "To learn more about them, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=312"
  },
  {
    "text": "check out \"Build spatial SharePlay experiences.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=314"
  },
  {
    "text": "Some apps may want to take advantage of SharePlay, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=318"
  },
  {
    "text": "but with content that not everyone has access to ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=320"
  },
  {
    "text": "before the activity begins. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=323"
  },
  {
    "text": "For this, try the new SharePlay file transfer APIs, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=325"
  },
  {
    "text": "which you can learn about more in \"Share files with SharePlay.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=329"
  },
  {
    "text": "By nature, SharePlay can mean something different ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=334"
  },
  {
    "text": "from app to app, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=337"
  },
  {
    "text": "depending on the experiences enabled. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=339"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's dive into some cool use cases ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=341"
  },
  {
    "text": "that can be enhanced with SharePlay. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=343"
  },
  {
    "text": "Adding SharePlay to an education app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=346"
  },
  {
    "text": "can help elevate static diagrams and text into interactive views ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=348"
  },
  {
    "text": "that stay in sync so students can engage together, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=352"
  },
  {
    "text": "no matter if they're far away or in the same classroom. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=355"
  },
  {
    "text": "Prep your meals for the week ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=359"
  },
  {
    "text": "to maximize your macros with your partner ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=360"
  },
  {
    "text": "and eat healthier together. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=363"
  },
  {
    "text": "Browse the latest feed to find the funniest new content. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=365"
  },
  {
    "text": "And if you combine everyone's interests, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=368"
  },
  {
    "text": "there will be something in there for everyone. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=370"
  },
  {
    "text": "Go shopping together. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=373"
  },
  {
    "text": "Figure out what furniture suits both your styles ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=375"
  },
  {
    "text": "before you move in with your new roommates. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=378"
  },
  {
    "text": "Coordinate a rideshare with friends. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=380"
  },
  {
    "text": "Browse the menu from your favorite takeout place together ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=383"
  },
  {
    "text": "and easily order family style. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=386"
  },
  {
    "text": "Take a moment to pause and think about the potential ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=389"
  },
  {
    "text": "of SharePlay in your app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=392"
  },
  {
    "text": "What group experiences have you thought about ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=393"
  },
  {
    "text": "or are already offered in your app today? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=395"
  },
  {
    "text": "Phew! ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=398"
  },
  {
    "text": "Lots of exciting use cases there. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=399"
  },
  {
    "text": "All this thinking's got me hungry.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=400"
  },
  {
    "text": "Priya Shah: Oh, hi, Justin, are you ordering lunch? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=404"
  },
  {
    "text": "Justin: Oh, hey, yeah, perfect timing! ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=406"
  },
  {
    "text": "I was just about to order some tacos ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=407"
  },
  {
    "text": "from that food truck down the street -- ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=409"
  },
  {
    "text": "they just adopted SharePlay. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=410"
  },
  {
    "text": "Priya: I love their tacos! Want to do a group order? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=412"
  },
  {
    "text": "Justin: Yeah, let's do it.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=414"
  },
  {
    "text": "Priya: Awesome! Could you add Gavin and Timirah too ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=422"
  },
  {
    "text": "so they can join our group order? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=424"
  },
  {
    "text": "Justin: Oh, yeah. Sure. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=426"
  },
  {
    "text": "Priya: I think I'm going to get the spicy tofu taco. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=428"
  },
  {
    "text": "Justin: I think I'm going to go with the chicken tinga taco. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=430"
  },
  {
    "text": "Priya: That sounds really good. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=431"
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, Timirah just added some chips and guac. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=432"
  },
  {
    "text": "Justin: I can't wait. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=434"
  },
  {
    "text": "Priya: I'm so excited. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=435"
  },
  {
    "text": "Justin: I'll see you in a minute. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=436"
  },
  {
    "text": "Priya: See ya. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=437"
  },
  {
    "text": "Starting a group order with Justin who was right next to me, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=439"
  },
  {
    "text": "and our friends who are on their way, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=442"
  },
  {
    "text": "was quick and seamless with SharePlay. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=444"
  },
  {
    "text": "And now I know I have some tacos to look forward to. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=446"
  },
  {
    "text": "SharePlay is a powerful feature ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=449"
  },
  {
    "text": "that can take any activity in your app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=450"
  },
  {
    "text": "and make it available for people to enjoy in groups ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=453"
  },
  {
    "text": "for a more engaging and interactive experience. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=455"
  },
  {
    "text": "By enabling real-time shared experiences like these, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=458"
  },
  {
    "text": "you can connect people in new ways ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=461"
  },
  {
    "text": "and provide them with a more social ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=463"
  },
  {
    "text": "and collaborative experience. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=465"
  },
  {
    "text": "Adopting SharePlay brings a group directly into your app, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=468"
  },
  {
    "text": "either to a shared experience you've already created ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=471"
  },
  {
    "text": "or to elevate an experience by making it possible ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=474"
  },
  {
    "text": "to now share with groups. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=477"
  },
  {
    "text": "If your app is currently full ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=479"
  },
  {
    "text": "of rich experiences for individuals, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=481"
  },
  {
    "text": "adopting SharePlay is a quick way to allow people ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=483"
  },
  {
    "text": "to experience your app with their friends and family. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=485"
  },
  {
    "text": "And if your app already supports group experiences, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=488"
  },
  {
    "text": "SharePlay can help make sharing seamless ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=491"
  },
  {
    "text": "by leveraging existing groups far and near ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=493"
  },
  {
    "text": "from FaceTime, Messages, and now, even AirDrop. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=496"
  },
  {
    "text": "SharePlay helps bring the group of friends ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=501"
  },
  {
    "text": "to your shared activity. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=503"
  },
  {
    "text": "Looks like Timirah just kicked off this week's social hour ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=505"
  },
  {
    "text": "with her favorite playlist. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=508"
  },
  {
    "text": "Anyone else in the group is also able to change the playlist. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=510"
  },
  {
    "text": "Once a group is in a SharePlay session, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=513"
  },
  {
    "text": "there is no need to reshare when switching activities. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=516"
  },
  {
    "text": "People can also completely change the activity type ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=519"
  },
  {
    "text": "without having to reconfigure the group. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=522"
  },
  {
    "text": "So a viral hit might remind Justin of an activity ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=525"
  },
  {
    "text": "in your app! ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=528"
  },
  {
    "text": "And if your app supports SharePlay, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=529"
  },
  {
    "text": "he can seamlessly bring the entire group with him ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=530"
  },
  {
    "text": "to check it out. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=533"
  },
  {
    "text": "And if anyone in the group doesn't already have your app, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=534"
  },
  {
    "text": "they are taken to the App Store to download it ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=537"
  },
  {
    "text": "if they'd like to join the group. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=539"
  },
  {
    "text": "Once you've added the group activity capability to your app, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=541"
  },
  {
    "text": "new this year in iOS 17, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=544"
  },
  {
    "text": "tapping the Share button from an active FaceTime call ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=546"
  },
  {
    "text": "presents a new, redesigned menu card ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=549"
  },
  {
    "text": "showcasing apps that support SharePlay ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=551"
  },
  {
    "text": "and collaboration experiences ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=554"
  },
  {
    "text": "to make it even easier for people ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=556"
  },
  {
    "text": "to step into your activity with friends. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=557"
  },
  {
    "text": "Adopting GroupActivities also provides your app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=560"
  },
  {
    "text": "with all the necessary group-management UI elements ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=563"
  },
  {
    "text": "like a people picker, notifications, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=566"
  },
  {
    "text": "and state changes, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=570"
  },
  {
    "text": "so you can focus on building an engaging activity. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=572"
  },
  {
    "text": "Additionally, by adopting SharePlay, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=575"
  },
  {
    "text": "you also get the real-time, low-latency, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=578"
  },
  {
    "text": "and fully encrypted data channel for syncing your app's activity. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=581"
  },
  {
    "text": "In order to leverage all of these benefits, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=585"
  },
  {
    "text": "let's take a look at adopting SharePlay. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=587"
  },
  {
    "text": "First, we will import the GroupActivities framework ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=590"
  },
  {
    "text": "and create an activity ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=593"
  },
  {
    "text": "which follows the GroupActivity protocol. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=594"
  },
  {
    "text": "We will then define the activity ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=597"
  },
  {
    "text": "with an activity identifier unique to this app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=599"
  },
  {
    "text": "Then we will add the activity metadata ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=602"
  },
  {
    "text": "which specifies parts of the shared experience ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=604"
  },
  {
    "text": "that are user facing -- ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=607"
  },
  {
    "text": "the title, the preview image, and the type. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=609"
  },
  {
    "text": "These details will show up in the UI ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=612"
  },
  {
    "text": "so everyone knows exactly which activity they are joining. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=614"
  },
  {
    "text": "You might have multiple activities in the same app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=618"
  },
  {
    "text": "So it's important to make sure the title and icon ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=620"
  },
  {
    "text": "are not generic. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=623"
  },
  {
    "text": "The title is the name of the activity the group started, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=625"
  },
  {
    "text": "not the name of the app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=627"
  },
  {
    "text": "And the optional subtitle lets you provide ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=629"
  },
  {
    "text": "even more detail about the activity. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=631"
  },
  {
    "text": "In this example, we've added the name of the taco truck ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=634"
  },
  {
    "text": "the order together activity is associated with. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=637"
  },
  {
    "text": "And the preview image is not the app's icon, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=640"
  },
  {
    "text": "but specific to the activity of ordering tacos together. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=643"
  },
  {
    "text": "Check out the SharePlay documentation ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=647"
  },
  {
    "text": "on developer.apple.com to implement starting, joining, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=649"
  },
  {
    "text": "and ending SharePlay experiences for your app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=653"
  },
  {
    "text": "And to learn how to use SharePlay ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=656"
  },
  {
    "text": "to adapt to your use case with GroupSessionMessenger, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=657"
  },
  {
    "text": "check out the session ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=660"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"Build Custom Experiences with Group Activities.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=661"
  },
  {
    "text": "Once you have the basic adoption of SharePlay complete, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=664"
  },
  {
    "text": "let's consider some best practices ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=667"
  },
  {
    "text": "to make your app's SharePlay experience magical and seamless. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=669"
  },
  {
    "text": "To build a great experience, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=673"
  },
  {
    "text": "it is important to design for your specific use case. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=675"
  },
  {
    "text": "Think about the experience you are creating ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=678"
  },
  {
    "text": "as if you and your friends are sharing it together ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=680"
  },
  {
    "text": "without any devices. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=682"
  },
  {
    "text": "How might you talk about a show together, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=684"
  },
  {
    "text": "order food together, or shop together? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=686"
  },
  {
    "text": "Take note of the parts of these experiences ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=690"
  },
  {
    "text": "that make you feel connected to the people ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=692"
  },
  {
    "text": "you're sharing them with. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=694"
  },
  {
    "text": "Add elements to your app's design ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=695"
  },
  {
    "text": "that might help preserve that feeling of togetherness. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=697"
  },
  {
    "text": "We dive deep into this topic in the session ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=701"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"Make a Great SharePlay Experience.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=703"
  },
  {
    "text": "When getting your app set up for SharePlay, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=706"
  },
  {
    "text": "it's also important to consider the different platforms ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=709"
  },
  {
    "text": "that your app supports. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=711"
  },
  {
    "text": "SharePlay is now available on iOS, iPadOS, macOS, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=713"
  },
  {
    "text": "and tvOS to ensure that anyone on any device ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=717"
  },
  {
    "text": "can join the experience you're building. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=721"
  },
  {
    "text": "With the addition of SharePlay through AirDrop, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=724"
  },
  {
    "text": "make sure to think about both types of SharePlay experiences, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=727"
  },
  {
    "text": "when people are apart and when they're close by. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=730"
  },
  {
    "text": "In order to make group activities in your app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=733"
  },
  {
    "text": "even more discoverable, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=736"
  },
  {
    "text": "support the ability to SharePlay directly in your app's UI ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=737"
  },
  {
    "text": "with a SharePlay button. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=740"
  },
  {
    "text": "Additionally, don't forget to adopt NSItemProvider ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=742"
  },
  {
    "text": "for your group activity. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=745"
  },
  {
    "text": "This will allow people to start a session with their friends ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=747"
  },
  {
    "text": "from the ShareSheet ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=750"
  },
  {
    "text": "and with friends nearby using AirDrop. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=751"
  },
  {
    "text": "Make sure that your metadata and state changes ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=754"
  },
  {
    "text": "are descriptive and understandable ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=756"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the context of someone using your app with their friends. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=758"
  },
  {
    "text": "This ensure everyone knows what's going on ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=762"
  },
  {
    "text": "with the activity. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=764"
  },
  {
    "text": "And finally, don't forget to test your experience. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=766"
  },
  {
    "text": "You will need two or more physical devices ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=769"
  },
  {
    "text": "for testing the SharePlay functionality effectively ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=771"
  },
  {
    "text": "to make sure everyone enjoying your activity ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=774"
  },
  {
    "text": "has the same incredible experience you had intended. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=776"
  },
  {
    "text": "Every app has an opportunity for SharePlay ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=780"
  },
  {
    "text": "SharePlay gives you access to existing groups from FaceTime, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=783"
  },
  {
    "text": "Messages, and now, even AirDrop. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=787"
  },
  {
    "text": "It provides a performant and private data channel ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=789"
  },
  {
    "text": "for syncing your app's data, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=792"
  },
  {
    "text": "and takes care of group management UI ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=794"
  },
  {
    "text": "like people pickers, notifications, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=796"
  },
  {
    "text": "and state management. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=798"
  },
  {
    "text": "When creating your own SharePlay experience, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=800"
  },
  {
    "text": "keep best practices in mind. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=802"
  },
  {
    "text": "We cannot wait to see ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=804"
  },
  {
    "text": "all the incredible SharePlay experiences you build. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=805"
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you for watching our session. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10239/?time=808"
  },
